Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再杠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又连杠了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣选择了自己一贯的打法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果这样就会败下阵来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是四筒  岭上开花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.22,0:00:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样的话  还是12000点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续杠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.97,0:00:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许要重生了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清一色  碰碰和  三暗刻  三杠子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤宝牌1  岭上开花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,32000点！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:21.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}番数役满
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:24.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}清澄高中  团体赛获胜…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲  祝贺你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  我赢了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能去全国大赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能和姐姐见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确实很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…我…赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
